some times we want to find out where our branch diverge
from main branch or some other branch,
what commits we have on this branch that does not exist on the other
we need to compare them!

what commit exist on bugfix/signup-form branch
that not exist on main branch?
before merging we should see this to find out what commits
we are transfer to main!

git log main..bugfix/signup-form    //all the commits on bugfix/signup-form
                                    //that not exist on main
                                    //the second one is the above one!

git log main..bugfix/signup-form  --oneline         //to see them briefly

git log bugfix/signup-form          //it's show all commits on
                                    //bugfix/signup-form branch!
                                    //it is different!

